{"tid":1238790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[洗腦] 女友爸爸最近開始用智能手機","createTime":"2019-06-18T02:57:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T04:21:34.000Z","uid":252975,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"544848fa7007543ed689df67f140b7e8f80716b2","tid":1238790,"uid":252975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:57:02.000Z","msg":"首先簡介女友爸爸背景，爸爸都始終幾大年紀，同佢食飯佢有傾下政治，知道共產黨、保皇黨唔好，害死好多人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近終於都換智能手機，係未爆華為單嘢前啲電話鋪強力推薦下出左華為。<br />\n有啲後悔無係依啲瑣碎事提出意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，女友爸爸開始好奇學玩新玩具。<br />\n但有件事搞唔明，點解係未安裝即時通訊 App 情況下，女友爸爸只係睇下 Youtube 同睇下跑馬 App <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近女友同我講，佢爸爸最近好鐘意睇 Youtube 啲「電腦聲中國假新聞」洗哂腦，仲要話習總做得好，管理得好等等。<br />\n咁就開口問女友爸爸點解睇依啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢話 Youtube 開著就有依啲嘢睇，所以極度懷疑本身出機前，已經有 Cache 或後門搞到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講野 1999 希望大家明解"},{"pid":"6008e7e3bb1613ee4cb1dfa701b0693efc9dbc42","tid":1238790,"uid":258566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:58:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02f617cfa3601e79dd251284c5598be143048f9d","tid":1238790,"uid":261530,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:58:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5217fc863af048a9c5d797281589f258cf365348","tid":1238790,"uid":252975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02f617cfa3601e79dd251284c5598be143048f9d","tid":1238790,"uid":261530,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T02:58:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:03:05.000Z","msg":"都無理由一打開就係... 除非本身屋企個 Network 有其他人睇過 Cache~"},{"pid":"6efb95454f563dbaf62225cfe1f34791ed500db7","tid":1238790,"uid":35946,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T03:05:46.000Z","msg":"出部新嘅